headline: 2 Toys & Games Stocks to Watch From a Challenging Industry
summary: HAS and MAT stand out as the Toys & Games industry navigates cost pressures, shifting demand and rising interest in STEM and emerging markets.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks with Impressive Fundamentals and 1 We Avoid
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
